{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Capital_Duel_and_Assault",
  "title": "A Capital Duel and Assault",
  "summary": "A small Republic strike force drops out of hyperspace to ambush a larger-than-usual Imperial convoy, sparking a running starfighter and capital-ship battle. Razor Squadron, led by Dante and flying alongside pilots Gren, Rebecca (Ghost 9), and Delede, screens the Nebulon-B frigate Eternal Vigilance while the Imperial ace Krieg picks off attackers in his TIE. Aboard the Vigilance, the captain Twila works the helm with grim relish as the medic Xar'on tends to the wounded, and Gren -- forced down in a crippled fighter -- is recovered and limps toward the bridge nursing a broken arm. The Y-wings and X-wings hammer the Imperial freighters in line while NPC fighters from both sides are battered back to their hangars. As the freighters begin fleeing the system, Dante orders the Razors to fall back and roost on the Nebulon, the battered scout pilots landing among the recovered Hornets as the engagement winds down.",
